<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_206_r2l31"><expan>Erſame<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / Als Jr vns vormals von <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Balthaſar<ex>en</ex></expan></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r2l33">von Maſpach ewrs mit <expan>Tumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vnd probſts cʒu Onlſpach 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_206_r2l32"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r2l34"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r2l35">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt </del> von der <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> als Jn Hans vnd Jacob die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r2l36">Topler auf das <expan>Lantger<ex>iht</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_206_line_1585991640904_349">hıe </ab></add> cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> geladen <expan>hete<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
</del>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_206" id="102v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Dem <expan>techand<ex>en</ex></expan> und capitel des
                            tums czu Wirczburg </del></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout"><expan>Ersame<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als ir uns vormals
                                                  von <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Balthasar<ex>en</ex></expan> von Maspach,
                                                  ewrs mit <expan>tumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> und
                                                  probsts czu Onlspach,
                                                  <add><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan></add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt,
                                                  von der <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, als in Hans und
                                                  Jacob die Topler auf das
                                                  <expan>lantger<ex>iht</ex></expan>
<add>hie</add> czu
                                                  <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> geladen
                            <expan>hete<ex>n</ex></expan>.</del><app>
<note><q type="endnote">...</q>Text bricht hier ab.</note>
</app></ab>
